<section class="page-hero">
        <h1>What we help with before you travel</h1>
        <p>From first questions to records and appointment planning, here is what our support includes at each stage.</p>
    </section>

    <main class="service-shell">
        <div class="phase-block">
            <div class="phase-side">
                <div class="phase-label">Before payment</div>
                <h2>Free case review</h2>
                <p>For patients who want a first conversation before choosing a paid service.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="phase-grid">
                <div class="phase-card">
                    <h3>Case intake</h3>
                    <p>We review your condition, timeline, preferred city, and what kind of help you may need.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="phase-card">
                    <h3>Direction</h3>
                    <p>We explain whether a shortlist, cost guidance, or hands-on coordination is the best next step.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="phase-card">
                    <h3>Expectation setting</h3>
                    <p>We explain what support we provide, what stays with the hospital, and when it makes sense to move forward.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="phase-block">
            <div class="phase-side">
                <div class="phase-label">Hospital Match &amp; Plan</div>
                <h2>Research support for self-directed patients</h2>
                <p>For patients who want a clearer shortlist of suitable hospitals and more confidence before committing to fuller support.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="phase-grid">
                <div class="phase-card">
                    <h3>Hospital shortlist</h3>
                    <p>We highlight hospitals and specialties that are more likely to fit your case, budget, and city preferences.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="phase-card">
                    <h3>Decision support</h3>
                    <p>We help you compare likely options, expected costs, and the practical side of treatment travel.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="phase-card">
                    <h3>Preparation material</h3>
                    <p>You receive practical guidance that helps you decide whether to continue on your own or move into active coordination.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="phase-block">
            <div class="phase-side">
                <div class="phase-label">Pre-Arrival Coordination</div>
                <h2>Hands-on coordination before hospital arrival</h2>
                <p>For patients who want help getting records ready, arranging appointments, airport pickup, and preparing for hospital arrival.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="phase-grid">
                <div class="phase-card">
                    <h3>Record handling</h3>
                    <p>We help prepare and translate records so the hospital side receives useful information before the first appointment.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="phase-card">
                    <h3>Appointment support</h3>
                    <p>We help coordinate with the hospital side so you can move toward the right consultation and next step.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="phase-card">
                    <h3>Pre-arrival planning</h3>
                    <p>We guide the key practical details before hospital arrival so the trip starts with less uncertainty.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="phase-block">
            <div class="phase-side">
                <div class="phase-label">What is not included</div>
                <h2>Boundaries of the service</h2>
                <p>Clear boundaries help patients understand exactly what they are paying for.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="phase-grid">
                <div class="phase-card">
                    <h3>Not hospital treatment</h3>
                    <p>Medical decisions, treatment plans, and hospital charges remain between you and the provider.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="phase-card">
                    <h3>Not an insurance policy</h3>
                    <p>We do not replace insurance, guarantee outcomes, or promise approval for any procedure.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="phase-card">
                    <h3>Not unlimited concierge</h3>
                    <p>Additional or extended support beyond package scope should be discussed separately so expectations stay clean.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

    <section class="service-note">
        <div class="service-note-box">
